export const  car=[

    {   
        color: "#115E59", 
        src :car1,
        name:"Beach Bum",
        url:"beach",
        price:80,
        type:"Rugged",
        sum:"The Modest Explorer is a van designed to get you out of the house and into nature. This beauty is equipped with solar panels, a composting toilet, a water tank and kitchenette. The idea is that you can pack up your home and escape for a weekend or even longer!"

    {  color: "#f68941",
        src :car2,
        name:"Modest Explorer",
        url:"modest",
        price:60,

        sum:"Beach Bum is a van inspired by surfers and travelers. It was created to be a portable home away from home, but with some cool features in it you won't find in an ordinary camper."

    {  color: "#161616", 
        src :car3,
        name:"Reliable Red",
        url:"relred",

        type:"Luxary",

    {   color: "#161616", 
        src :car4,
        name:"The Cruiser",
        url:"cruiser",
        price:120,
        type:"Luxary",
        sum:"Dreamfinder is the perfect van to travel in and experience. With a ceiling height of 2.1m, you can stand up in this van and there is great head room. The floor is a beautiful glass-reinforced plastic (GRP) which is easy to clean and very hard wearing. A large rear window and large side windows make it really light inside and keep it well ventilated."

    {   color: " #115E59",
         src :car5,
        name:"Green Wonder",
        url: "green",
        price:70,

        sum:"The Cruiser is a van for those who love to travel in comfort and luxury. With its many windows, spacious interior and ample storage space, the Cruiser offers a beautiful view wherever you go."

    {  color: "#f68941",
         src :car6,
        name:"Dream Finder",
        url: "dream",
        price:65,
        type:"Simple",
        sum:"With this van, you can take your travel life to the next level. The Green Wonder is a sustainable vehicle that's perfect for people who are looking for a stylish, eco-friendly mode of transport that can go anywhere."

export default {car, }
